'''Slaver permits''' were legal documents issued by the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] to [[slaver guild]]s for a fee, and were designed to regulate the slave trade throughout [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]]. Some slave trading organizations, such as the [[Zygerrian Slavers Guild]], were able to acquire permits at a reduced cost due to their size and structure.

